                <note rend="inline" type="source">875.6363/104: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Albania</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Swift</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tirana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-08-03T16:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1923—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received August 4—2:09 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>47. Albanian Parliament convenes extraordinary session August 20th for discussion
                    of oil concessions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Swift</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
